## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="54576-122">发音词典是集合的词或短语以及使用适当的发音字母指定其发音。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="54576-122">A pronunciation lexicon is a collection of words or phrases together with their pronunciations specified using an appropriate pronunciation alphabet.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="54576-123">此方法通常称为平台基础结构以响应<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis>基于应用程序调用<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A>和使用由当前实现的合成语音<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="54576-123">This method is typically called by the platform infrastructure in response to a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> based applications calling <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> and using the synthesizer voice implemented by the current <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> instance.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="54576-124">值`mediaType`通常是一种 MIME 规范，SSML 规范用于 MIME 媒体规范处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="54576-124">The value of `mediaType` is typically a MIME specification, as the SSML specification uses MIME for media specifications.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="54576-125">实现<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A>使用<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>接口传入的要从资源加载词典。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="54576-125">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> uses the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed in to load a lexicon from a resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="54576-126">然后将存储`System.IO.Stream`到中词典`System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`实例，由词典 URI 编制索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="54576-126">It then stores a `System.IO.Stream` to the lexicon in a `System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary` instance, indexed by the lexicon URI.</span></span>  

```  
public static Dictionary<Uri, Stream> _aLexicons = new Dictionary<Uri, Stream>();  

 public void AddLexicon(Uri uri, string mediaType, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
    Stream stream = site.LoadResource(uri, mediaType);  
    _aLexicons.Add(uri, stream);  
}  

 public void RemoveLexicon(Uri uri, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
     Stream stream;  
     if (_aLexicons.TryGetValue(uri, out stream)) {  
         stream.Close();  
         _aLexicons.Remove(uri);  
     }  
}  

```



